contentfulProduct.title: Luxe Organic Waffle Thermal Hoodie

content.value:
Mix & Match Organic Waffle Crew, Organic Waffle Henley or Organic Waffle Hoodie
Buy 3, save $5
Buy 5, save $15
This waffle hoodie features a zip-up closure and a warm, cozy thermal fabric that makes it easy to layer. Made from a blend of organic cotton and recycled polyester. Super comfy for everyday wear.
Material: 60% Organic Cotton/ 40% Recycled Polyester
Organic cotton is certified by OCS (Organic Content Standard) which ensures that the fibers aren't treated with pesticides, insecticides, herbicides, and conserve more natural resources like water
Recycled polyester is certified by GRS (Global Recycled Standard) which dramatically lowers its environmental impact by diverting used plastic from landfills and oceans, while consuming less energy
Dyeing, washing, manufacturing process are certified under OCS (Organic Content Standard) & RCS (Recycled Claim Standard).
Produced in a Sedex-certified factory which adheres to strict social and ethical compliance
Origin: Zhangjiagang, China
Model is 5'9" and wearing a size Medium
Machine wash cold. Gentle cycle. Do not bleach. Tumble dry low. Cool iron or dry clean if needed.
